    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After discussing it IRL, we think that it's an edge that would only happen if the user doesn't use the hits widget nor define the `hitsPerPage` attribute using the initial search parameters in the instantsearch constructor. So it should be fixed in the documentation and not in the widget.\n",
